Linear
============
--- Loi giai chi tiet phan (a) ---
1. Kiem tra tu ma toan 0...
   -> Co ton tai tu ma toan 0.
2. Kiem tra tinh dong voi phep XOR...
   -> Vi pham: 011 XOR 101 = 110 (Khong thuoc tap ma).
Ket luan: Day KHONG phai ma tuyen tinh.
============
0000
0111
1001
1110
============
--- Loi giai chi tiet phan (b) ---
Ma tran kiem tra H (2x3):
1 1 0 
0 1 1 
1. Phan tich khong gian nghiem cua H...
   Do dai ma (n): 3
   So chieu ma (k): 1
2. Sinh tat ca 2^k = 2 tu ma...
3. Tap day du cac tu ma:
   000
   111
Ket luan: Da sinh thanh cong 2 tu ma.
============
